span.p:
SERVER-AUTHORITATIVE + CLIENT PREDICTION
predict locally for feel, reconcile to server truth;
the FPS / shooter standard

SERVER-AUTHORITATIVE, ZONED/SHARDED
interest management + area-of-interest replication;
consistency & scale over latency

SERVER-AUTHORITATIVE (single sim)
clients send intent, server is truth;
anti-cheat + consistency, moderate counts

DETERMINISTIC LOCKSTEP
exchange inputs, each peer simulates identically;
tiny bandwidth for thousands of units, needs determinism

STATE SYNC / SNAPSHOT INTERPOLATION
replicate state with interpolation buffer;
simple, latency-tolerant co-op / casual
